dct_title_s: Adelaide, public transport map [cartographic material] / Prepared for the Minister of Transport by the Director-General of Transport. Compilation: T.J. Wilson. Cartography: R. s. K. Tan (Verso)
dct_description_sm: Minister of Transport. Folded title: Adelaide public transport map; bus, train, tram services. Inset maps of "Noarlunga," "Elizabeth," and "Central area" on verso. Map includes index of tram, bus, railway services, information about contacts to services and museums.
dct_publisher_sm: Adelaide, Printed by Mitchell Press for A.B. James, Govt. Printer 1973.
